<< **14. MANUFACTURING: ANYTHING OLDER THAN A VW BUG? - NBC NEWS (US)

We're doing a story about the last VW Beetle Bug. It will be produced at the

Puebla, Mexico, factory soon. Our question: Can anyone name a modern piece

of machinery that has been around longer, basically unchanged, than the

Beetle? The Beetle Bug was first built 1938-1940 (depending on start date

